Package: sdschooldata
Title: Fetch and Process South Dakota School Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Al", "Martin", , "almartin@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Downloads and processes school data from the South Dakota Department
    of Education (SD DOE). Provides functions for fetching enrollment data from
    Fall Census counts and transforming it into tidy format for analysis.
    Supports historical data from 2006 to present.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
Depends:
    R (>= 4.0)
Imports:
    dplyr,
    readxl,
    readr,
    purrr,
    stringr,
    tidyr,
    rlang,
    httr,
    rappdirs
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    knitr,
    rmarkdown,
    ggplot2,
    scales
VignetteBuilder: knitr
Config/testthat/edition: 3
URL: https://github.com/almartin82/sdschooldata
BugReports: https://github.com/almartin82/sdschooldata/issues
